<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>233</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Lungdeih muol liemna phamsa vangkhuo chu,
 Ka en ngam puoi heiloh pak thieka;
 Lungmuon siktui a dawn diu ka ngai ngam puoi,

[V2]
 Albang kavai ui na chun leh zuo,
 Na len-guolte mel ka en ngam puoi;
 Tuoi lung deih tello, suihlung a hel ngei.

[V3]
 2. Chun leh zuo lo in bangtin a um dem?
 Zing khawvak, muikhuo thim bang zin in;
 Ka vawnsen chun telloin muong thei puona.

[V4]
 3. Sietlei gamtin muoltin tawh mah lengle
 Vawnsen nang tawh lenna sau neu hi;
 Lunggil hihgim leh lunghelna a suok tai.

[V5]
 4. Kumsawt Elsadai vangkhuo tuolnuom chu
 Muh ka nuom, ka vawnsen tuollenna,
 Chunnu ngailo ninnuom tuol a lenna.</lyrics>
<title>Phamsa Vangkhuo</title>
</song>